headline: Syssero, Inc. Named Workday Services Partner
summary: Syssero, Inc, a consulting firm, today announced it has signed a partnership agreement with Workday (NASDAQ: WDAY), a leading provider of solutions to help organizations manage their people and money. This partnership with Workday brings access to advanced resources and tools, and the capability to offer even more customized services and support to fit the unique needs of each client.
